p: \rI feel like I should say, once more... this isn't personal.
\rI just want what's best for my people.
\rWhat I meant by "we're battling by my rules"...
\rIn the Distortion World, typings work... a little differently.
\rSo we're going to play by the typings I know, not yours.
\rThis battle will be the Inverse of everything you thought you knew!
\rThe loser will be sent back to their own world, unable to return here again.
\rThe crystal shards are on the line.
\rLet's begin, \pn! The fates of the worlds rest with us!
\rI've never seen battling like that before, ever.
\rEven recordings of trainers like Steven and Red don't compare to what I saw.
\r\pn. Nyx said she was going to use the crystal to bring Giratina back to its true power.
\rDo you think... do you think it's possible to take it down?
\rIt's a legendary Pokemon made even more powerful by a shard of Nyx's Crystal.
\rIf anyone could do it, it's you, \pn.
\r\pn... I don't know what to say.
\rI can't imagine how much pressure you're under.
\rBut... if there was anyone in the universe I'd pick to save us, it would be you.
\r\pn, I can't handle Giratina on my own, especially not with that crystal.
\rBut you just took down someone from another universe! If anyone can do it, you can.
\rGo. Go be the hero I know you are!
\r\pn... you just singlehandedly took down every cult in the region, and then Giratina.
\rI think it might finally be time to admit you're better than me.
\r...there's still loads for us to do though.
\rI'm sure there's a lot of cult members who don't know their leaders have been defeated.
\rI'll start cleaning up the mess. It's the least I can do to feel helpful.
\rGo battle the Elite Four! I mean, at this point, you're already a Pokemon Master, but it'd be nice to make it official, you know?
\rI'd be suprised if there was anything you couldn't do.
\rYou can get to Victory Road through Nexa Town.
\rI think you have to go through Narra Town to get through to Nexa, though.
\rYou're the closest friend I've ever had.
A mysterious force blocks the exit.
\bThe big threat that's been terrorizing our reality since the beginning of time.
\bI'll take those crystals off your hands for now.
\bI'll return them to their rightful place... but honestly, I don't think they'll be there for long.
\bNow that Nyx was defeated... well, the extradimensional threat is gone, and you'd probably be the best person to guard against human ones.
\bSo come see me after you've defeated the Pokemon League. You know where to find us.
